headline: eBay, Bumble, Revolve, and Shutterstock Shares Are Falling, What You Need To Know
summary: A number of stocks fell in the afternoon session after the broader U.S. stock market declined amid investor caution and a pullback in technology stocks. The main story? Investors are cashing in on a good run and feeling a bit cautious.
